msgctxt "an6.57:14.2"
msgid ""
"Idhānanda, ekacco ucce kule paccājāto hoti—khattiyamahāsālakule vā "
"brāhmaṇamahāsālakule vā gahapatimahāsālakule vā, aḍḍhe mahaddhane mahābhoge "
"pahūtajātarūparajate pahūtavittūpakaraṇe pahūtadhanadhaññe."
msgstr ""
"It’s when some person is reborn in an eminent family—a well-to-do family of "
"aristocrats, brahmins, or householders—rich, affluent, and wealthy, with "
"lots of gold and silver, lots of property and assets, and lots of money and "
"grain."

msgctxt "an6.57:14.3"
msgid ""
"So ca hoti abhirūpo dassanīyo pāsādiko paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya "
"samannāgato, lābhī annassa pānassa vatthassa yānassa mālāgandhavilepanassa "
"seyyāvasathapadīpeyyassa."
msgstr ""
"And they’re attractive, good-looking, lovely, of surpassing beauty. They get "
"to have food, drink, clothes, and vehicles; garlands, fragrance, and makeup; "
"and bed, house, and lighting."

msgctxt "an6.57:14.4"
msgid ""
"So kāyena duccaritaṃ carati, vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, manasā duccaritaṃ "
"carati."
msgstr "But they do bad things by way of body, speech, and mind."

